---
title: "_setAssetOut (BaseAuction)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_live: _whenNoLiveAuctions()
    q_check_live --> q_revert_live: liveAuctionExists
    q_revert_live --> q_error: revert LiveAuction()
    q_check_live --> q_check_zero: no live auctions
    q_check_zero --> q_revert_zero: assetOut == address(0)
    q_revert_zero --> q_error: revert InvalidZeroAddress()
    q_check_zero --> q_check_same: assetOut != address(0)
    q_check_same --> q_revert_same: currentAssetOut == assetOut
    q_revert_same --> q_error: revert ValueNotUpdated()
    q_check_same --> q_update: currentAssetOut != assetOut
    q_update --> [*]: s_assetOut = assetOut; delete s_assetParams[currentAssetOut]; emit AssetOutSet

    note right of q_update
        INV-013: Old assetOut params are deleted when assetOut changes
    end note

    q_error --> [*]
